headline.print_headline: In Blow to Abe, Japan Trade Minister to Resign Over Funds Scandal: Media
headline.main: In Blow to Abe, Japan Trade Minister to Resign Over Funds Scandal: Media

lead_paragraph: In a blow to Prime Minister Shinzo Abe, Japan's newly appointed trade and industry minister plans to resign following reports that some of her support groups misused political funds, Japanese media said on Saturday.
